  ('bookkeeper-moex-02019', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-099-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '全台公司於 X5年1月1日折價發行十年期公司債一批，原擬採利息法攤銷折價，但誤用直線法。此項 攤銷方法之誤用，在 X6年初，對下列項目會造成何種影響？', '["公司債帳面價值高估，保留盈餘高估", "公司債帳面價值低估，保留盈餘低估", "公司債帳面價值高估，保留盈餘低估", "公司債帳面價值低估，保留盈餘高估"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d423e3df13ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f9ce5ef6f193", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099220", "c": "602", "s": "300", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年建築師、技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-02020', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-099-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '乙公司於X1年1月1日發行5年期自X1年12月31日起平均分期清償公司債$10,000，X4年12月31日 資產負債表應如何表達此公司債？', '["流動負債$2,000，無長期負債", "流動負債$10,000，無長期負債", "流動負債$2,000，長期負債$8,000", "流動負債$1,000，長期負債$2,000"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d423e3df13ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f9ce5ef6f193", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099220", "c": "602", "s": "300", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年建築師、技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-02021', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-099-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '保全公司核准發行100,000股面額$1普通股，實際發行40,000股，以每股$5全數由摩根購入，此外，並 無其他股票發行，此時：', '["摩根擁有保全公司40%股權", "保全公司應承認$160,000的獲利", "保全公司普通股股本為$200,000", "保全公司普通股股本為$40,000"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d423e3df13ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f9ce5ef6f193", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099220", "c": "602", "s": "300", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年建築師、技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-02022', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-099-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司淨資產$400,000，投入資本$250,000，發行並流通在外普通股 25,000 股，由前述資料可知下列那 一項敘述一定成立？', '["保留盈餘$400,000", "每股帳面價值$16", "累積虧絀$250,000", "每股帳面價值$10"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d423e3df13ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f9ce5ef6f193", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099220", "c": "602", "s": "300", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年建築師、技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
